direction: right

cat: Server catalog { icon: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/heroicons@2.1.1/24/outline/rectangle-group.svg }
pol: Policy engine { icon: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/heroicons@2.1.1/24/outline/shield-check.svg }
aud: Audit store { icon: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/heroicons@2.1.1/24/outline/clipboard-document-list.svg }
inc: Incident response { icon: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/heroicons@2.1.1/24/outline/exclamation-triangle.svg }

cat -> pol
pol -> aud
aud -> inc
inc -> cat: tighten catalog
